{"tid":622072,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［LIVE]4日3夜波蘭遊記","createTime":"2018-04-08T23:36:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-09T15:18:15.000Z","uid":181122,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"899045c20d6df5709910ea55b86882273747ba6f","tid":622072,"uid":181122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T23:36:48.000Z","msg":"因為最近放緊假 所以決定同朋友去個小旅行 <br />\n一開始係諗住去Warsaw 但最後多謝連登巴打絲打令我地改變主意去Krak&oacute;w 我地都係諗住chill下咁去 所以無特別追景點<br />\n<br />\nDay 1 London - Krak&oacute;w <br />\n<br />\n因為我哋要搭朝早機 所以就要好早起身 仲差啲因為去錯巴士站而miss咗班coach 好彩下一班個司機比我哋上車先唔會遲到<br />\n<br />\n搭咗一個鐘頭車到就到咗Stansted airport 因為係窮遊 所以我哋選擇咗搭英國版hong kong express -Ryan air<br />\n<br />\n一去到因為要visa check 條隊勁長 用咗好多時間先輪到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/065043_4e0c6819dbf4d26b744619898626ac64.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F065043_4e0c6819dbf4d26b744619898626ac64.png&h=da8ac72f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n經過多種嘅障礙 終於可以上機嚕<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/065252_ab8b8d2b7db8782fb21fd0273f966217.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F065252_ab8b8d2b7db8782fb21fd0273f966217.png&h=a7176ea9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一上機梗係訓啦 訓到咁上下就land咗<br />\n<br />\n我哋以飛快嘅速度的過埋security 就去搭巴士去Airbnb 點知我哋又去錯咗巴士站 兩個on99咁又等咗一陣先發覺去錯咗巴士站 兩條友都唔知想點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n經過半個鐘嘅車程終於到咗airbnb<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/065442_a3a324165bab6f0cfc153554349fe63f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F065442_a3a324165bab6f0cfc153554349fe63f.png&h=9024cf17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尼到簡直係試正版嘅劏房 幾舒服又幾抵<br />\n<br />\n我哋抖左一陣之後就出發去搵嘢食 我哋去咗一個廢墟附近 嗰度有好多唔同嘅餐廳 我哋就求其入咗去一間意大利餐廳 眼闊肚窄嘅我哋嗌咗個炸魷魚之後仲嗌咗兩個大pizza 好飽 個Pizza真係好大個<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/065630_f20c02ed1a53c5ac7f50ff47258ca088.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F065630_f20c02ed1a53c5ac7f50ff47258ca088.png&h=c1c90812&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/065653_e84961b2e61529f65d3b930a4c10bc3b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F065653_e84961b2e61529f65d3b930a4c10bc3b.png&h=1faa8b51&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩個Pizza 一個炸魷魚加兩杯嘢飲都係係港幣大約＄250 認真咁嘅價錢香港邊度食到<br />\n<br />\n食完之後我哋決定行返去old town個邊周圍行下 雖然今日係星期日 但沿路行返去都好多當地人係度食雪糕飲咖啡飲啤酒<br />\n<br />\n好飽嘅我哋都叫咗2球雪糕食 我叫咗raspberry同coffee都唔錯<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/070546_e6d1b2eb4749f3a262e81b7b5ae92140.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F070546_e6d1b2eb4749f3a262e81b7b5ae92140.png&h=9878249c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n決定一路行一路食<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/070743_4c926ff253603f9e98f5d8bf44109889.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F070743_4c926ff253603f9e98f5d8bf44109889.png&h=dfe3fb2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/070928_f7277ee40337d7d440fd5e5c5f94ce0d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F070928_f7277ee40337d7d440fd5e5c5f94ce0d.png&h=d1cf173d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一個好chill嘅旅行又點少得coffee time呢<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/071503_c516f19bc09501ab4e2e6bdae6ce6bf1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F071503_c516f19bc09501ab4e2e6bdae6ce6bf1.png&h=afca1888&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n飲飽食醉後就行人啦 之後去咗一個類似market嘅行仔 入面有啲特色krak&oacute;w特產 恐龍 黃色珠寶 鹽燈<br />\n<br />\n之後我哋頂唔順返左去訓教 醒左之後 重點行程來了<br />\n<br />\n我哋竟然去食日本嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n入到啲裝修都幾靚嘅 但一見到個menu就心知不妙同埋見唔少人都好似食泰國嘢 <br />\n<br />\n我哋就叫咗個&rsquo;炸牛肉&rsquo;拉麵諗住唔會差得去邊啦<br />\n<br />\n一嚟到個賣相都幾靚<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/072605_749b5d4d876f19116ed90fb45874ce56.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F072605_749b5d4d876f19116ed90fb45874ce56.png&h=2e44097a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點知 飲左第一啖個湯 就想大叫一聲 好難食呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n湯底係不知明味道 <br />\n<br />\n麵質係好似公仔麵 仲衰過出前一丁 <br />\n<br />\n牛又唔知咩質地難食 好似牛肉做嘅午餐肉咁<br />\n<br />\n啲筍個味又勁怪 我都幾鐘意食筍但都唔想食<br />\n<br />\n豆又唔好食又唔係好夾 唔知想點<br />\n<br />\n淨係得個蛋食得落口<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/09/072912_d2884413694106ff249ab8ec0b077aa4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F09%2F072912_d2884413694106ff249ab8ec0b077aa4.png&h=0d02fb57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋拿拿聲食晒可以食得落肚嘅野 就頭也不回咁走咗 真係好難食 好彩佢地啲物價唔貴 無咁心痛<br />\n<br />\n我哋食完都夜 周圍基本上啲野都閂晒 所以我哋就返去airbnb休息 睇下電視搵定聽日去鹽礦嘅資料 就訓教了<br />\n<br />\n聽日見"},{"pid":"5a3c926f3db68a7ee5f6019aa29ece596caada66","tid":622072,"uid":105517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T23:53:09.000Z","msg":"巴打 我都係波蘭窮遊緊 有無興趣約埋一齊玩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27b2fa0e0cbd46b67eff33386e93da1379c78ace","tid":622072,"uid":50576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T00:16:11.000Z","msg":"波蘭妹呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"698296e83dade427a389a3f914f86402b6659fd2","tid":622072,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T01:31:47.000Z","msg":"Day1就食亞洲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e11b5b7d0c7bb6adba6209853287c6c81dee9833","tid":622072,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"698296e83dade427a389a3f914f86402b6659fd2","tid":622072,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T01:31:47.000Z","msg":"Day1就食亞洲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T01:38:26.000Z","msg":"本身喺英國生活既話應該唔會想食西餐既欲望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81416adb884634fad83025e17366801eb090f45d","tid":622072,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e11b5b7d0c7bb6adba6209853287c6c81dee9833","tid":622072,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"698296e83dade427a389a3f914f86402b6659fd2","tid":622072,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T01:31:47.000Z","msg":"Day1就食亞洲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T01:38:26.000Z","msg":"本身喺英國生活既話應該唔會想食西餐既欲望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T01:44:29.000Z","msg":"咁又唔係，去到Day4食返餐都好正常，第一日就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有，當越餓既時假，亂入餐廳，中伏既機會越高，這個法則全球適用<br />\n<br />\nBTW，英國既野食&hellip;&hellip;真心唔會食到有癮"},{"pid":"481a65ff3fc08bf2f4c0a560ef500fd2834af77e","tid":622072,"uid":145361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T02:15:29.000Z","msg":"食下波蘭菜ma"},{"pid":"7ec97826c85d16a865aa28bf13466d15fa113494","tid":622072,"uid":181122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27b2fa0e0cbd46b67eff33386e93da1379c78ace","tid":622072,"uid":50576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T00:16:11.000Z","msg":"波蘭妹呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T10:59:33.000Z","msg":"等我睇下有無先"},{"pid":"743517203c9ba1846b9f6c2cdd81b3cd565f8501","tid":622072,"uid":181122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"698296e83dade427a389a3f914f86402b6659fd2","tid":622072,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T01:31:47.000Z","msg":"Day1就食亞洲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T11:00:17.000Z","msg":"呢度好多日本野咪想試試 點知好伏"},{"pid":"ad5191fa07ea8bf78ba8a1d95099aaeaf073f99a","tid":622072,"uid":181122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81416adb884634fad83025e17366801eb090f45d","tid":622072,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e11b5b7d0c7bb6adba6209853287c6c81dee9833","tid":622072,"uid":141782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"698296e83dade427a389a3f914f86402b6659fd2","tid":622072,"uid":28195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T01:31:47.000Z","msg":"Day1就食亞洲野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-09T01:38:26.000Z","msg":"本身喺英國生活既話應該唔會想食西餐既欲望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/